# History of Google

Google was founded in **1998** by **Larry Page** and **Sergey Brin** while they were PhD students at Stanford University.

Initially, Google was created as a **search engine** to organize information on the internet and make it easily accessible to everyone.

Over time, Google expanded into many products such as:
- Gmail
- Google Maps
- Google Chrome
- Android

Today, Google operates under its parent company **Alphabet Inc.** and is one of the most influential technology companies in the world.

