  # History of Amazon

Amazon was founded in **1994** by **Jeff Bezos** in Seattle, USA.

It started as an **online bookstore**, but gradually expanded into selling a wide variety of products.

Amazon later introduced:
- Amazon Prime
- Kindle
- Amazon Web Services (AWS)

Today, Amazon is one of the worldâ€™s largest **e-commerce and cloud computing companies**.

